<div id="introbox">
<div class="introprimtext">
<p class="introprimtextlongtext">
CoverSutra gives you a handy and attractive way to control iTunes without ever leaving your current app. See what's currently playing, pause and resume playback, change songs, and even enjoy your album's artwork without being interrupted from your work.</p>
</div><!--closes introprimtext-->
